text:
Today, both you and I worked hard, y'all!
Good job, Producer!

Thank you, Kogane.
Thanks for joining me for dinner after work.

I'm fine, thank ya kindly!
Eatin' delicious food every day makes me happy!

Haha.
As long as Kogane's satisfied.

Oh, 283PRO-san!
What a coincidence to meet you here!

Do you have time after this? If you're free,
would you like to have a meal together?
